title: december 14: black out on golden gate
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the time the lights went out on the Golden Gate Bridge, and about the building of the bridge itself. Afterwards, she talks about the founding of a record label. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
